<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Anando Ghose</title>
  
  <!-- Favicon -->
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.png" type="image/png">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.png" type="image/png">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/favicon.png">
  
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    :root {
      --blue-link: #0000FF;
      --text-dark: #000000;
    }
    
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      height: 100vh;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .container {
      position: relative;
      height: 100vh;
      width: 100vw;
    }
    
    .background {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background-image: url('/mac-background.png');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      z-index: -1;
    }
    
    .content {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50px;
      left: 50px;
      z-index: 10;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .email-link {
      display: block;
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: var(--blue-link);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    .about {
      max-width: 450px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .social-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .social-link {
      color: var(--blue-link);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .social-link i {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }
    
    .social-link:hover {
      opacity: 0.8;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    
    .sr-only {
      position: absolute;
      width: 1px;
      height: 1px;
      padding: 0;
      margin: -1px;
      overflow: hidden;
      clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
      white-space: nowrap;
      border-width: 0;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .content {
        top: 30px;
        left: 30px;
        right: 30px;
      }
      
      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
      
      .email-link {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
      }
      
      .about {
        max-width: 100%;
      }
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .content {
        top: 20px;
        left: 20px;
        right: 20px;
      }
      
	  .social-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .social-link {
        color: var(--blue-link);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .social-link i {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .social-link:hover {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        background-color: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      }

      /* Additional style if you want text labels alongside icons */
      .social-link-with-text {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 8px 16px;
      }

      .social-link-with-text span {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="background"></div>
    <div class="content">
      <h1>Anando Ghose</h1>
      <a href="mailto:me@anandoghose.com" class="email-link">Email me</a>
      
      <p class="about">
        Building automations for finance reporting & analytics. 
        <br/>Tech enthusiast who loves turning complex problems into elegant solutions.
        <br/>Self-taught programmer. MBA from the Indian School of Business.
      </p>
      
      <div class="social-links">
		<a href="https://substack.com/@anandoghose" class="social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
			<i class="fa-solid fa-newspaper"></i><span class="sr-only">Substack</span>
		  </a>
		  <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/anandoghose/" class="social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
			<i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i><span class="sr-only">LinkedIn</span>
		  </a>
		  <a href="https://instagram.com/your-profile" class="social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
			<i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i><span class="sr-only">Instagram</span>
		  </a>
		  <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCb8LzmczkHjCz0Bhvgg-QjA" class="social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
			<i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i><span class="sr-only">Youtube</span>
		  </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>